collectionMetadata.name: Number of Active CPF Members by Age Group as at end of Year
collectionMetadata.description:
An active CPF member refers to a person who has at least 1 CPF employment contribution 
paid for him for the current or for any of the preceding 3 months. 

Figures exclude all self-employed persons. 

Figures are rounded to the nearest ten.
